posting_body: ['WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM EASY TO  QUALIFY!', 'Quick move in.', 'If you are an independent worker have low credit or background issues and have problems finding a place to settle with your family, do not hesitate call me or TEXT me, I am a rental expert in South Florida, I will find a property for you and get you approved.', 'WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM with credit score of over 550, we will buy any property CASH for you  up tp $600,000 and then rent it to you for 1 to 3 years until you can get ready to purchase it, it will save some of your rent money towards the purchase ( about 25% of payment).', 'Stunning 2 bedrooms 2 baths Tower Suite with breathtaking Ocean, Intracoastal, City and Turnberry Golf Course views.', 'Beautiful residence located on the top 29th floor features spacious layout with floor to ceiling windows, wide terrace, marble floors, updated kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances, custom walk-in closets, breakfast and formal dining areas.', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'I RESPOND INMIDIATELLY!!', 'show contact info', ')', '""EASY SOLUTIONS REALTY LLC ""']
